// DP: a number i has the same set bits as i>>1, plus 1 if its lowest bit is set.
public int[] CountBits(int n) {
    var bits = new int[n + 1];
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        bits[i] = bits[i >> 1] + (i & 1);
    return bits;
}
```
**Complexity:** O(n) time, O(n) space (for the output array).

